  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:452px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Evenfall_Hall.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/32/Evenfall_Hall.jpg/450px-Evenfall_Hall.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"258\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/32/Evenfall_Hall.jpg/675px-Evenfall_Hall.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/32/Evenfall_Hall.jpg/900px-Evenfall_Hall.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Evenfall_Hall.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Evenfall Hall by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://jordigart.blogspot.com/\">Jordi Gonzalez</a> ©.</div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Stormlands.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The stormlands and the location of Evenfall Hall\"><img alt=\"The stormlands and the location of Evenfall Hall\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/The_Stormlands.png/400px-The_Stormlands.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"274\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/The_Stormlands.png/600px-The_Stormlands.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/The_Stormlands.png/800px-The_Stormlands.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 30%; left: 89.2%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -6px; top: -6px; width: 12px; font-size: 12px;\"><img alt=\"The stormlands and the location of Evenfall Hall\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Evenfall Hall\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/18px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/24px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 120%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Evenfall Hall</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a> and the location of Evenfall Hall\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Evenfall Hall</b>, or simply <b>Evenfall</b>, is the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarth\" title=\"House Tarth\">House Tarth</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is located on the western coast of the island of <a href=\"/index.php/Tarth\" title=\"Tarth\">Tarth</a> along <a href=\"/index.php/Shipbreaker_Bay\" title=\"Shipbreaker Bay\">Shipbreaker Bay</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_west.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_west.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Evenfall_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a> visited Evenfall Hall during his <a href=\"/index.php/Royal_progress\" title=\"Royal progress\">royal progresses</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthree_heads_had_the_dragon_-_governance_under_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthree_heads_had_the_dragon_-_governance_under_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_of_Tarth\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brienne of Tarth\">Brienne of Tarth</a> was trained by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Goodwin\" title=\"Goodwin\">Goodwin</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Master-at-arms\" title=\"Master-at-arms\">master-at-arms</a> of the castle.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Evenfall_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_1\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 1\">Chapter 1</a>, Jaime I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafthe_west.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_west.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, The West.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text